MultiPartMime
=============

Net::HTTP does not have native support for multi-part mime attachments.  This plugin adds the support
to Net::HTTP.

Taken from http://pivots.pivotallabs.com/users/damon/blog/articles/227-standup-04-27-07-testing-file-uploads,
wrapped up into a plugin.


Dependencies:

  * Net::HTTP
  * MIME::Types (mime-types gem)

